  },
  {
    question: "How do these technologies work together?",
    answer: "CBCT imaging allows us to precisely plan implant placement and identify optimal bone sites. Ozone therapy sterilizes the surgical site and promotes healing. Ceramic implants with PRF provide biocompatible tooth replacement with enhanced healing. Together, these technologies offer the safest, most predictable outcomes."
